    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/8ae014432aa458dc5eb37e386ebffebf.poster.avif?t=1769066152\" width=1170 height=510 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/8ae014432aa458dc5eb37e386ebffebf.webm?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/8ae014432aa458dc5eb37e386ebffebf.mp4?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定制船只</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工欲善其事，必先利其器！为你的海盗船装配各种不同的武器、工具和传奇遗物——身为船长，你可以自由地设计海盗船的布局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/dceb3cb13d23f007f41b36e216edc0a9.poster.avif?t=1769066152\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/dceb3cb13d23f007f41b36e216edc0a9.webm?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/dceb3cb13d23f007f41b36e216edc0a9.mp4?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开抢！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与不同势力磋商交易，或是轰沉他们的船只来抢走战利品——谁知道呢，或许你还会撞上大运，发现远古的藏宝图！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/6d5f5521b965933e7c29ad29eae4e7b2.poster.avif?t=1769066152\" width=1170 height=510 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/6d5f5521b965933e7c29ad29eae4e7b2.webm?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/6d5f5521b965933e7c29ad29eae4e7b2.mp4?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态升级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现、强化、连携！几乎所有东西都可以被升级——然后通过巧妙的装备组合，发挥出数十倍的效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/58168f2d17a22d2a070a17ba61cf223f.poster.avif?t=1769066152\" width=1170 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/58168f2d17a22d2a070a17ba61cf223f.webm?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/58168f2d17a22d2a070a17ba61cf223f.mp4?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >海盗基地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造属于你自己的海盗藏身地，在存放战利品的同时，还可以在大海上扩张你的影响力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/50d9b35da8e927589c5dcb953bf55531.poster.avif?t=1769066152\" width=1170 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/50d9b35da8e927589c5dcb953bf55531.webm?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/50d9b35da8e927589c5dcb953bf55531.mp4?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >纵横四海</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同船只、不同的游戏目标、神秘的深海之谜、还有数不尽的装备——《拼拼凑凑海盗帮》的设计理念，就是提供极高的重复可玩性！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/8030d0db85f063c730ccb8e931615c8b.poster.avif?t=1769066152\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/8030d0db85f063c730ccb8e931615c8b.webm?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/8030d0db85f063c730ccb8e931615c8b.mp4?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏正在积极开发中，您可以加入我们的Discord社区来分享创意，或是在YouTube上关注开发日志。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/aeedca7ab13b3b3a9bdf801ef653ad36.poster.avif?t=1769066152\" width=1170 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/aeedca7ab13b3b3a9bdf801ef653ad36.webm?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327000/extras/aeedca7ab13b3b3a9bdf801ef653ad36.mp4?t=1769066152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
